Package: libbc-allocators-dev
Architecture: amd64
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         libbc-core-dev (>= 1.0.0)
Description: bc-* ecosystem memory allocators (development files)
 Pool (general-purpose), arena (bump-pointer with reset),
 slab (fixed-size), a user-facing context object threading leak
 callbacks and statistics, plus a growable typed-array primitive.
 .
 This package ships the static library, public headers, and
 pkg-config descriptor required to build against bc-allocators.
